Really? I thought you wanted to be
a member of our family.

580
00:53:10,920 --> 00:53:11,760
I'm Cousin Prom.

581
00:53:12,719 --> 00:53:13,639
Prom what?

582
00:53:13,719 --> 00:53:14,800
Prompat, sweetie.

583
00:53:39,719 --> 00:53:42,840
Auntie Oonruean, I'm going downstairs
to find something to eat.

584
00:53:43,559 --> 00:53:44,719
Please go ahead.

585
00:53:44,800 --> 00:53:45,639
I'll come too.

586
00:53:53,199 --> 00:53:54,119
Want another bite?

587
00:53:57,760 --> 00:53:58,960
Don't you want more?

588
00:54:00,280 --> 00:54:01,360
Khim?

589
00:54:02,119 --> 00:54:02,960
Are you full?

590
