592
00:54:12,559 --> 00:54:14,000
-Yes.
-Let me put that away.

593
00:54:15,159 --> 00:54:17,119
It's okay, Auntie Oon. I'll do it.

594
00:54:18,360 --> 00:54:19,719
-Thank you.
-Sure.

595
00:54:21,559 --> 00:54:22,840
Shall we get some food?

596
00:54:25,400 --> 00:54:26,599
Okay.

597
00:54:35,920 --> 00:54:36,840
What are you doing?

598
00:54:44,880 --> 00:54:48,559
It's the dinner menu.
Khim asked me to order something.

599
00:54:53,639 --> 00:54:55,760
All right. Please go ahead.

600
00:55:11,800 --> 00:55:13,079
INPATIENT FOOD MENU

601
00:55:24,199 --> 00:55:25,719
I'm going to England with Khim.

602
00:55:25,800 --> 00:55:27,440
You take care of business here.

603
00:55:28,800 --> 00:55:30,159
Don't worry about work.

604
00:55:31,360 --> 00:55:32,239
Worry about this.

605
00:55:34,519 --> 00:55:36,360
My people at the jail told me

606
00:55:37,320 --> 00:55:39,159
that a stranger visited Gaogla.

607
00:55:40,480 --> 00:55:42,239
Uncle, can you guess who?

608
00:55:49,360 --> 00:55:52,559
Hello, I'd like to visit
Mr. Gaogla Chayodom.

609
00:55:52,639 --> 00:55:53,599
Please open your bag.

610
00:55:57,599 --> 00:56:00,719
I knew that annoying girl would betray us.

611
00:56:09,960 --> 00:56:11,159
I've brought news.

612
00:56:12,400 --> 00:56:14,000
I don't think you'll like it.

613
00:56:16,239 --> 00:56:17,400
Your baby is gone.

614
00:56:20,119 --> 00:56:22,159
Is that good news or bad?

615
00:56:23,320 --> 00:56:26,800
Khim wants to talk to you,
so she wrote you a letter.

616
00:56:28,119 --> 00:56:31,280
She wants to hear the truth
from you and no one else.

617
00:56:36,159 --> 00:56:38,079
I miscarried a few days ago.

618
00:56:39,679 --> 00:56:41,880
I couldn't let it be born
to a father like you.

619
00:56:42,880 --> 00:56:44,519
Since you brought us shame,

620
00:56:45,840 --> 00:56:48,639
it's better that the baby not be born
to bear that shame.

621
00:56:50,199 --> 00:56:52,400
I need to get my life back.

622
00:56:54,079 --> 00:56:55,039
The time we've had,

623
00:56:55,679 --> 00:56:59,199
consider it payment for the bad deeds
we committed in our past lives.

624
00:57:00,360 --> 00:57:02,079
I don't want to sink any lower.

625
00:57:08,880 --> 00:57:10,760
Now I know we're too different.

626
00:57:13,000 --> 00:57:16,840
If you can still behave like a gentleman,
please sign our divorce papers.

627
00:57:18,039 --> 00:57:19,800
I want a clean break.

628
00:57:20,920 --> 00:57:24,039
After we sign the papers,
we can go our separate ways.

629
00:57:25,119 --> 00:57:26,960
I'm not asking too much, am I?

630
00:57:48,920 --> 00:57:51,079
I guess she wants to get rid of me fast.

631
00:57:52,039 --> 00:57:53,519
Khim's worried about you.

632
00:57:53,599 --> 00:57:55,639
She's worried I won't die!

633
00:57:55,719 --> 00:57:58,239
Hey! I'm just the messenger.

634
00:57:58,320 --> 00:58:00,039
Just write your reply.

635
00:58:00,119 --> 00:58:02,840
Tell her to come here
if she wants a divorce.

636
00:58:03,840 --> 00:58:05,559
I'm in jail because of her.

637
00:58:05,639 --> 00:58:07,719
Why do I have to throw my life away here?

638
00:58:08,679 --> 00:58:12,079
If she loved herself,
why would she resort to this?

639
00:58:12,920 --> 00:58:14,639
She can go live where she wants.

640
00:58:14,719 --> 00:58:17,239
But she can't just act
like my life means nothing!

641
00:58:53,079 --> 00:58:54,239
What have you two done?

642
00:58:59,800 --> 00:59:02,400
I gave you access to this home

643
00:59:02,480 --> 00:59:04,320
so that Saikhim could vent to you.

644
00:59:05,119 --> 00:59:06,159
But you betrayed me.

645
00:59:06,239 --> 00:59:08,000
You tried to help them make up.

646
00:59:09,559 --> 00:59:11,360
So this means yesterday's letter…

647
00:59:11,440 --> 00:59:12,519
It was fake.

648
00:59:16,519 --> 00:59:19,280
-Guard, show her in.
-This way, please.

649
00:59:22,400 --> 00:59:23,639
GAOGLA

650
00:59:26,920 --> 00:59:29,679
Tell her to come here
if she wants a divorce.

651
00:59:30,280 --> 00:59:32,519
No wonder he mentioned a divorce.

652
00:59:33,320 --> 00:59:35,159
You switched the letters.

653
00:59:35,239 --> 00:59:38,920
You know very well
that he's not good enough for Saikhim!

654
00:59:39,440 --> 00:59:41,079
Why would you help them rehash this?

655
00:59:41,880 --> 00:59:43,519
Why did you do this?

656
00:59:44,440 --> 00:59:46,599
If you really wanted the best for Saikhim,

657
00:59:47,639 --> 00:59:51,119
you'd protect her
from that good-for-nothing man!

658
01:00:00,000 --> 01:00:01,119
You're the only one

659
01:00:01,199 --> 01:00:02,960
who knows all about Saikhim.

660
01:00:04,000 --> 01:00:07,679
If you promise me
that you'll keep everything secret

661
01:00:07,760 --> 01:00:10,960
and keep him out of Saikhim's life,

662
01:00:12,199 --> 01:00:13,039
I promise

663
01:00:13,679 --> 01:00:16,039
I'll pay for you
to study in England with her.

664
01:00:30,159 --> 01:00:31,360
Yes, you're uncomfortable.

665
01:00:32,480 --> 01:00:34,119
It's like betraying your friend.

666
01:00:34,639 --> 01:00:36,079
But you know, deep down,

667
01:00:36,159 --> 01:00:38,760
that he's not suitable for Saikhim at all.

668
01:00:41,119 --> 01:00:43,440
Good friends want the best for each other.

669
01:00:44,159 --> 01:00:45,360
Isn't that right?

670
01:00:45,960 --> 01:00:49,760
Prove to me
that you're truly Saikhim's friend.

671
01:00:51,159 --> 01:00:53,280
Have fun with your new life.

672
01:00:53,360 --> 01:00:56,320
Here's a map and the keys. There.

673
01:00:57,079 --> 01:00:59,920
I got this phone for you
as a surprise present.

674
01:01:00,000 --> 01:01:04,719
Hey, I signed you up to a dating service
and picked five local guys for you.

675
01:01:06,800 --> 01:01:09,079
Why is this happening to me?

676
01:01:11,199 --> 01:01:14,360
I never should have let this happen, Lita.

677
01:01:15,760 --> 01:01:19,159
-How could I let this happen?
-It's not your fault, Khim.

678
01:01:21,360 --> 01:01:24,760
It's my fault.
I brought those men into your life.

679
01:01:30,800 --> 01:01:32,159
You got her pregnant,

680
01:01:32,800 --> 01:01:34,760
but that doesn't mean you own her.

681
01:01:34,840 --> 01:01:36,320
What century are we in?

682
01:01:37,280 --> 01:01:40,039
Don't use the baby
to bring her down to your level.

683
01:01:41,719 --> 01:01:42,920
If I hadn't been careless,

684
01:01:43,440 --> 01:01:45,159
you'd never have slept with her.

685
01:01:46,679 --> 01:01:47,920
Remember this.

686
01:01:48,000 --> 01:01:50,599
Never dare to touch
this forbidden fruit, ever.

687
01:01:52,960 --> 01:01:57,480
If you promise me
you'll keep him out of Saikhim's life,

688
01:01:58,119 --> 01:01:59,159
I promise

689
01:01:59,920 --> 01:02:02,239
I'll pay for you
to study in England with her.

690
01:02:22,079 --> 01:02:22,920
He said

691
01:02:24,079 --> 01:02:25,039
he wants a divorce.

692
01:02:31,760 --> 01:02:32,599
Really?

693
01:02:34,760 --> 01:02:35,840
An actual divorce?

694
01:02:39,360 --> 01:02:41,559
He said he doesn't wanna rehash things.

695
01:02:43,719 --> 01:02:44,920
He doesn't care anymore.

696
01:02:50,480 --> 01:02:52,280
He doesn't want to explain anymore.

697
01:02:54,719 --> 01:02:59,239
No matter what you think of him,
he doesn't care anymore.

698
01:03:20,920 --> 01:03:22,440
It all started because of me,

699
01:03:23,880 --> 01:03:25,199
and it'll end with me.

700
01:03:25,880 --> 01:03:29,360
No one wanted that child,
so it should all end here.

701
01:03:32,719 --> 01:03:35,039
TRAISIT'S CASH ON WHEELS
TRADE YOUR CARS FOR CASH

702
01:03:35,119 --> 01:03:36,559
-Let's go now.
-All right.

703
01:03:37,400 --> 01:03:38,480
Hey, watch out!

704
01:03:39,320 --> 01:03:40,159
Hey!

705
01:03:41,719 --> 01:03:42,559
It's my fault

706
01:03:43,079 --> 01:03:44,960
for thinking money didn't matter.

707
01:03:45,039 --> 01:03:47,840
Counselor, who knows
if this money will help Gla's case?

708
01:03:48,480 --> 01:03:51,480
